{"tid":1889270,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】防暴警確診肺炎　記者必須追問PK強有無出席退休派對！！！","createTime":"2020-02-20T14:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T17:50:39.000Z","uid":272572,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1ff1f1535d2e56b9fe835742bb7cded52666f0","tid":1889270,"uid":272572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"各位記者，咪話聽日唔識問問題質班官，今次真係關乎公眾利益<br />\n<br />\n而家有傳媒估計，武肺黑警有出席西九警區指揮官的退休派對，假如無估錯即係西九龍總區指揮官卓孝業。<br />\n<br />\n咁西九龍總區指揮官咁高級，退休派對鄧炳強唔會唔出席掛?　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n接任西九龍總區指揮官嘅陶輝又有無去?　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他警隊高層包括Er Er Sir、謝振中又有無去?　<br />\n<br />\n如果咁多膠層出席，一齊HAPPY，係極有可能惹到武肺<br />\n你睇吓「邊爐家族」搞到幾咁大鑊？<br />\n<br />\n如果咁多膠層出事，出事架嘛<br />\n請記者必須追問：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 佢哋係咪卓孝業退休派對?<br />\n2. 有幾多警隊高層有份出席，包括鄧炳強、陶輝、Er Er Sir、謝振中等?<br />\n3. 佢哋是否要隔離? （唔會唔需要掛?　出事架喎）</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E6%B2%B9%E7%BE%8E%E8%8B%91%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A-%E6%8E%A5%E8%BC%89%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E5%82%B3%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258B%2591%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25BC%2589%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%2F&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=fbdb0cdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258B%2591%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25BC%2589%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%2F&h=c9b64a69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E6%B2%B9%E7%BE%8E%E8%8B%91%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A-%E6%8E%A5%E8%BC%89%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E5%82%B3%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n根據《蘋果日報》報道，病人駐守北角警署，2月18日發燒，最近出席西九警區指揮官的退休派對，地點疑是醫管局總部對面的九龍城警署，據悉聚會有超過60人參加。<br />\n雖然報道未有提及是那一位指揮官退休，但翻查資料顯示，西九龍總區指揮官卓孝業原訂於今年2月正式退休，在反送中運動期間，較知名事件是處理去年11月長達13天的理大攻防戰。"},{"pid":"47f8802123ca2cb476a0965873682e7e5c8ad445","tid":1889270,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"點會冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c809f8693bfa52e0cbff15aad1b46664ea59e708","tid":1889270,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"大家集氣<img src=\"/assets/face